name: The Matter of Britain
description: Christmas is on the horizon in Arkham and many of its residents have taken to the streets in an unnatural shopping frenzy. Brace against the winter weather and spread the goodwill of the season to the city — but an omniscient eye watches over you, so you’d better be good for goodness sake.
